metadata.description:
Infinati and Dubdelay have joined forces to create Iris.

Iris is an electrifying and captivating track that seamlessly blends the groovy beats of house music with the futuristic soundscapes of psybass. The pulsating basslines and intricate rhythms will keep you moving on the dance floor, while the hypnotic melodies and trippy effects will take you on a journey through the cosmos.
metadata.name: Infinati & Dubdelay - Iris
